CURRENTLY, PPCWNY HAS HEALTH CENTERS IN BUFFALO, WEST SENECA, NIAGARA FALLS, NORTH TONAWANDA, ROCHESTER, SYRACUSE, GREECE, BATAVIA, CANANDAIGUA AND WHEATFIELD HAS APPROXIMATELY 40,600 VISITS ANNUALLY. ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp.Desc: RAPE CRISIS SERVICE (RCS) PROVIDED 1,500 SURVIVORS OF SEXUAL ASSAULT AND THEIR SIGNIFICANT OTHERS COUNSELING AND SUPPORT IN MONROE, GENESEE, LIVINGSTON, ORLEANS AND WYOMING COUNTIES, ENGAGED OVER 8,000 PEOPLE THROUGH COMMUNITY EDUCATION PROGRAMS AND PROFESSIONAL TRAININGS, COLLABORATED WITH THE SUNY GENESEO HELP ESTABLISH SEXUAL ASSAULT COUNSELING AND SUPPORT SERVICES TO STUDENTS, COLLABORATED WITH IBERO AMERICAN ACTION LEAGUE TO HELP SERVICE YOUNG LATINA GIRLS WHO HAVE BEEN AFFECTED BY SEXUAL ASSAULT.

ProgSrvcAccomActy3Grp.Desc: IN CONTROL, A TEEN PREGNANCY PREVENTION PROGRAM IN ROCHESTER, EMPOWERED OVER 1,000 INNER CITY TEENS THROUGH EDUCATIONAL, VOCATIONAL AND RECREATIONAL PROJECTS, TEENS PARTICIPATED IN TWO COLLEGE TOURS (IN ROCHESTER AND WASHINGTON, DC). OTHER ACTIVITIES FOR YOUTH INCLUDED PHOTOGRAPHY, DANCE, COLOR GUARD, DRUM CORE, MUSIC AND THEATER DEVELOPMENT AND COMMUNITY SERVICE PROJECTS.

ProgSrvcAccomActyOtherGrp.Desc: EDUCATION AND OUTREACH PROVIDES PROGRAMMING EDUCATIONAL PROGRAMMING ON SEXUAL AND REPRODUCTIVE HEALTH ACROSS OUR REGION. EDUCATION AND OUTREACH PROVIDED APPROXIMATELY 600 EDUCATION PROGRAMS TO OVER 23,400 CHILDREN, TEENS AND ADULTS. DEVELOPED A TRAINING CURRICULUM FOR CONNECT & BREATHE (A NEWLY LAUNCHED, NON-BIASED TALK LINE IN ROCHESTER) "LISTENING LINE" VOLUNTEERS. PROVIDED EDUCATIONAL PROGRAMS TO OVER 400 WOMEN AT THE ALBION CORRECTIONAL FACILITY.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: DONORS HAVE SPECIFIED THAT EARNINGS ON PLANNED PARENTHOOD'S ENDOWMENT ARE UNRESTRICTED AS TO THEIR USE. PLANNED PARENTHOOD'S POLICY IS TO UTILIZE ITS ENDOWMENT EARNINGS, AS CONSIDERED NECESSARY AND IN ACCORDANCE WITH REGULATIONS, TO SUPPORT PLANNED PARENTHOOD'S OPERATING ACTIVITIES IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE DONORS INTENT. THE BOARD HAS APPROVED A SPENDING RATE BASED ON THE AVERAGE MARKET VALUE OF THE ENDOWMENT FOR THE PAST 20 QUARTERS. THE ANTICIPATED SPENDING IS EXPECTED TO BE NO MORE THAN 5% OF THE AVERAGE MARKET VALUE OF THE ROLLING AVERAGE, PROVIDING THE CORPUS REMAINS INTACT.

SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE FINANCE COMMITTEE REVIEWS THE RETURN WITH THE CFO AND THE FORM 990 AND SUPPLEMENTAL FORMS ARE SENT TO ALL BOARD MEMBERS PRIOR TO FILING.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 12C
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: EACH BOARD MEMBER IS REQUIRED TO COMPLETE A CONFLICT OF INTEREST STATEMENT ANNUALLY. EACH STATEMENT IS THEN REVIEWED BY THE PRESIDENT OF THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION B, LINE 15
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: OFFICER AND KEY EMPLOYEE COMPENSATION IS REVIEWED ANNUALLY AND PLANNED PARENTHOOD PARTICIPATES IN A PAY FOR PERFORMANCE REVIEW AND REWARD SYSTEM ANNUALLY. IN THE COMMUNITY, PLANNED PARENTHOOD IS AWARE OF THE CURRENT EMPLOYMENT COSTS FOR PERSONS WITH MEDICAL SPECIALTIES. PPCWNY IS IN COMPETITION WITH ACTIVE HEALTH SYSTEMS IN THE GREATER ROCHESTER, BUFFALO AND SYRACUSE AREA AND OFFERS REASONABLE WAGES TO RETAIN TALENTED INDIVIDUALS.

SupplementalInformationDetail.FormAndLineReferenceDesc: FORM 990, PART VI, SECTION C, LINE 19
SupplementalInformationDetail.ExplanationTxt: THE ANNUAL AUDITED FS, THE IRS 990 INFORMATION RETURN, AND THE NYS CHAR 500 ARE AVAILABLE ON THE WEBSITE OF THE OFFICE OF THE ATTORNEY GENERAL OF NYS. IN ADDITION, THE OFFICE OF PLANNED PARENTHOOD OF CENTRAL AND WESTERN NEW YORK'S CFO WILL FAX, MAIL OR SEND A SCANNED COPY OF THE SAME DOCUMENTS UPON REQUEST FROM AN INDIVIDUAL.
THE BOARD OF DIRECTORS TAKES RESPONSIBILITY FOR THE AUDIT AND REVIEWS AUDIT RESULTS ON AN ANNUAL BASIS. NO CHANGES HAVE BEEN MADE TO THIS POLICY.
